name: Menat (Street Fighter V)
description:
Menat from Street Fighter 5

There is already a great LoRA of Menat made by Murky, but his didn't had the holiday costume which is my favorite, so i trained her as well.

This Lora supports 3 of Menat's costumes, classic, holiday and mummy

  • for classic costume use "menat_classic" and add to your prompt

    • bodysuit, shorts, thighhighs, circlet, navel cutout, shawl

  • for mummy costume use "menat_mummy" and add to your prompt

    • hood, bell, red dress, bare shoulders, paw gloves, tail

  • for holiday costume use "menat_holiday" and add to your prompt

    • hood, bell, red dress, bare shoulders, paw gloves, tail

You may also want to add "dark skin, green eyes, egyptian, bob cut", to your Prompt.

Trained on Nai


Can be used at 1.0 weight

All images were generated using yabalMix (https://civitai.com/models/28648/yabalmix) with xformers on and using kl-f8-anime2 vae.

images were generated at 512x768 and upscaled using highres fix by 1.95 and using 4x_foolhardy_Remacri upscaler
